cycle The Tide Turns Widdershins

direction-counterclockwise

Careen blue
  Beach the ship and scrape the hull
  clean of barnacles and weed.

Provision green
  Take on fresh water, salt pork,
  and powder for the guns.

Set Sail orange
  Catch the ebb tide and stand out
  for the shipping lanes.

Return to Port red
  Fence the plunder and pay the crew
  before the whole rig starts anew.
